BUT I REFUSE TO KEEP
COMING BACK JUST TO BE

00:34:22,854 --> 00:34:25,357
- ATTACKED EACH TIME I DO.
- ALL RIGHT, WHOA.
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

00:34:25,398 --> 00:34:27,692
YOU WERE WORKING WITH SHANE,
