A RESEMBLANCE

00:41:43,712 --> 00:41:47,007
TO ONE OF THESE HEAPS.
YOU DIG?

00:41:51,052 --> 00:41:52,429
I'M HAVING TROUBLE,
MANNY,

00:41:52,470 --> 00:41:54,222
