WHEN MY SON WAS BORN.

00:42:20,081 --> 00:42:23,126
YEAH. THAT TREE DOESN'T
BEAR FRUIT ANYMORE.

00:42:23,168 --> 00:42:25,712
AH, SPEAKING OF SUCH,

00:42:25,754 --> 00:42:29,049
HAVE YOU HEARD
FROM VINNY LATELY?

00:42:30,133 --> 00:42:31,634
