ENTERTAIN CLIENTS
AT THEIR HOME.

00:42:51,279 --> 00:42:53,114
AND SHE FEELS--
I DON'T KNOW--

00:42:53,156 --> 00:42:54,491
THAT I WOULDN'T
BE COMFORTABLE.

00:42:54,532 --> 00:42:56,034
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

00:42:56,076 --> 00:42:57,619
WHAT THE HELL DO THEY
HAVE TO BE EMBARRASSED ABOUT?

00:42:57,660 --> 00:42:59,537
I MEAN, YOU FOUGHT
WAY PAST YOUR PRIME.

00:42:59,579 --> 00:43:01,998
